{"tid":2010722,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"成人網站睇球星？熱搜榜出爐！","createTime":"2020-05-10T14:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T09:54:06.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c108cfbfffe44fb430aa1faa385bcc531e8ba0a0","tid":2010722,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T14:58:34.000Z","msg":"著名色情網站PORNHUB日前公布，2019年站內搜尋次數最多嘅足球員排名榜，C朗拿度同美斯繼續雄霸頭2位，至於第3位就由阿根廷前鋒莫路伊卡迪爆冷奪得。<br />\n<br />\n去色情網站睇球星聽落相當騎呢，不過上榜球員又的確係魅力十足，好似「冠軍」C朗拿度就出晒名身材勁Fit，佢嘅CR7底褲品牌廣告更加係勁Sexy，至於C朗死敵美斯就憑「鄰家男孩」形象，成功進佔第2位。第3位就有效力巴黎聖日耳門嘅莫路伊卡迪，呢位阿根廷前鋒成身紋身夠晒野性，而且佢老婆Wanda同樣以「著得少」見稱，相信莫路伊卡迪可以進佔三甲，老婆都有唔少功勞。<br />\n<br />\n第4位開始分別有阿歷斯山齊士、基利安麥巴比、保羅戴巴拿、夏薩特、史達寧、賓施馬，英格蘭「萬人迷」碧咸雖然已經退休多年，但仍然可以躋身第10位。"},{"pid":"9a950b119253123ad11b1ea886273877e52415f0","tid":2010722,"uid":16659,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T14:59:04.000Z","msg":"基利安麥巴比 史達寧 賓施馬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df56c5f389ac85fd1d545879e5b7450dd0d0b66","tid":2010722,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T15:01:20.000Z","msg":"無連加特？"},{"pid":"ae0098e954318b84b18150ee68806628c66fe0f4","tid":2010722,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a950b119253123ad11b1ea886273877e52415f0","tid":2010722,"uid":16659,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T14:59:04.000Z","msg":"基利安麥巴比 史達寧 賓施馬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T15:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a88cc57f040556d5b758d36b91413b85cb0412","tid":2010722,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0